{"tid":2142459,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"果然好打得！ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-08-06T11:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T11:59:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f3200dd9c9a3f5d49061caa979216966eca78141","tid":2142459,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T11:59:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200722/SSHMCUUKEZAMTODSQ3B7GOCFQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200722%2FSSHMCUUKEZAMTODSQ3B7GOCFQE%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOvulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=c17624e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200722%2FSSHMCUUKEZAMTODSQ3B7GOCFQE%2F&h=1595d2ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200722/SSHMCUUKEZAMTODSQ3B7GOCFQE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n果然好打得！ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x9h3mDyrIp44Hd0e6zbXcCKFIC8=/1280x771/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TOBUHG5NNVD7PBFSV3MZEJ2DLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx9h3mDyrIp44Hd0e6zbXcCKFIC8%3D%2F1280x771%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTOBUHG5NNVD7PBFSV3MZEJ2DLM.jpg&h=853743d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又到了「好打得」表演外行打低內行的時間了，跟過往無數次一樣，無論專家說甚麼，她都永遠不聽，我行我素，把錯誤堅持到底。<br />\n<br />\n這一次，包括何栢良、袁國勇、梁子超、許樹昌、馬仲儀等人在內的專家一致指出，全民檢測無助抗疫，因為最大的風險來自豁免檢疫人士入境。<br />\n<br />\n外來人士豁免檢疫，全港巿民則要做檢測，這是甚麼邏輯呢？而且，即使檢測當下是陰性，仍有免檢疫人士入境，把風險帶入香港，離開檢測中心後，陰性者也有可能馬上受病毒感染。<br />\n<br />\n全民檢測除了浪費資源及擾民外，還有甚麼後果，暫時不作揣測。但政府有甚麼動機，則不妨看看以下事實：<br />\n<br />\n提供核酸檢測服務的三間機構不經公開招標，而由港府指定。<br />\n<br />\n三間機構之一的「中國檢驗」有逾30年歷史，不過不好意思，過去30年，該公司不是做醫務檢測，而是驗車及機電產品。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一間叫連城醫療投資公司，連城比中檢資格老一些，在中檢成立前兩天成立。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「好打得」不是浪得虛名的，。。。。。。。。。"}]}